"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Recovery of the longitudinal component of magnetization to its equilibrium value is exponential with a time constant T",
"    <sub>",
"     1",
"    </sub>",
"    . T",
"    <sub>",
"     1",
"    </sub>",
"    depends upon field strength, temperature, and tissue composition.",
